          .source
            %H3 Share thy code
            %p 
              The source for this site is 
              %br
              =link "free to download.", "http://github.com/jasoncale/jasoncaledotcom/tree/", "Fork on Github"
              It is a simple
              =link "Sinatra", "http://sinatrarb.com", "Awesome hackers framework" 
              app written in 
              =link "Ruby", "http://www.ruby-lang.org/en/", "My programming language of choice"
              and is hosted using 
              =link "Heroku.", "http://heroku.com/", "Super quick ruby platform"
